      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778844304318,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "browser-runtime-skill/\n├─ SKILL.md                         # Agent 使用说明：何时用、如何申请/释放、失败处理\n├─ README.md                        # 项目架构与本地运行方式\n├─ broker/                          # 常驻控制服务：leases/jobs/tab groups/artifacts\n├─ extension/                       # Chrome companion extension：真实 Tab Group 操作\n├─ cli/                             # runtimectl / leasectl / fetch-page\n├─ extractors/                      # 站点脚本：probe/extract/workflow\n├─ runtime/                         # Docker compose、launch config、profile mount 约定\n├─ artifacts/                       # 截图、HTML、trace、日志（gitignore）\n├─ data/                            # sqlite lease/job state（gitignore）\n└─ docs/                            # 操作协议、并发模型、风险策略",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f1_OdxyNJWxfM4dSeZWR",
      "originalText": "browser-runtime-skill/\n├─ SKILL.md                         # Agent 使用说明：何时用、如何申请/释放、失败处理\n├─ README.md                        # 项目架构与本地运行方式\n├─ broker/                          # 常驻控制服务：leases/jobs/tab groups/artifacts\n├─ extension/                       # Chrome companion extension：真实 Tab Group 操作\n├─ cli/                             # runtimectl / leasectl / fetch-page\n├─ extractors/                      # 站点脚本：probe/extract/workflow\n├─ runtime/                         # Docker compose、launch config、profile mount 约定\n├─ artifacts/                       # 截图、HTML、trace、日志（gitignore）\n├─ data/                            # sqlite lease/job state（gitignore）\n└─ docs/                            # 操作协议、并发模型、风险策略",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 254
    },
